{"word":"κοσμέω","slug":"κοσμέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰοσμέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κόσμος\">κόσμος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘put in order’, <b>tidy <a href='B:470 12:44'>Mt 12:44</a>; <a href='B:490 11:25'>Lk 11:25</a>; trim,</b> so as to have lamps ready <b><a href='B:470 25:7'>Mt 25:7</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘effect a pleasant appearance’, <b>make attractive, adorn <a href='B:470 23:29'>Mt 23:29</a>; <a href='B:490 21:5'>Lk 21:5</a>; <a href='B:610 2:9'>1 Ti 2:9</a>; <a href='B:630 2:10'>Tit 2:10</a>; <a href='B:670 3:5'>1 Pt 3:5</a>; <a href='B:730 21:2'>Rv 21:2</a>, <a href='B:730 21:19'>19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κόρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κοσμικός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}